## Recommended Structure (What Goes Where)

- `tech_stack.md`: versions, package managers, runtime requirements, build/test commands
- `product_brief.md`: goals, constraints, non-goals, user flows (optional)
- `patterns/`: architecture and design patterns (API standards, error handling, auth, etc.)
- `guides/`: how we work (coding standards, testing strategy, upstream sync, AI workflow)
- `workflows/`: checklists for common tasks (new feature, bug fix, refactor, code review)
- `specs/`: lightweight work-item specs (optional). If you use Spec Kit, feature specs live under `specs/###-feature/` at repo root instead.

